import React from 'react';
import './navbar.css';
import Emblem from '../../../media/logo-img.png';
import {Container, Nav, Navbar, Image} from 'react-bootstrap';

function Navigation() {
    return (
        <>
            <Navbar className = "main-navbar d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" collapseOnSelect expand = "lg" fixed = "top" variant="dark">
                <Navbar.Brand className = "emblem" href="#home"><Image src = {Emblem} fluid></Image></Navbar.Brand>
                <Container className = "mx-0">
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav"></Navbar.Toggle>
                    <Navbar.Collapse>
                        <Nav className = "mr-auto">
                            <Nav.Link className = "mr-3" href = "/#about">About</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link className = "mr-3" href = "/#features">Features</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link className = "mr-3" href = "/#stats">Stats</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link className = "mr-3" href = "/#pricing">Pricing</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link className = "mr-3" href = "/#media">Media</Nav.Link>
                        </Nav>
                        <Nav>
                            <Nav.Link className = "mr-3" href = "/login">Login</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link className = "mr-3" href = "/register">Register</Nav.Link>
                        </Nav>
                    </Navbar.Collapse>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
    </>
    )
}

export default Navigation
